<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Semangat Kerjanya Sayang! ✨</title>
    <style>
        @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@300;400;600&family=Sacramento&display=swap');

        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ffe5ec 0%, #ffc2d1 100%);
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 20px;
            overflow-x: hidden;
        }

        .container {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.75);
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            padding: 40px 30px;
            border-radius: 24px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(229, 107, 135, 0.2);
            text-align: center;
            max-width: 450px;
            width: 100%;
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.4);
            animation: fadeIn 1.5s ease-in-out;
        }

        h1 {
            font-family: 'Sacramento', cursive;
            font-size: 3.5rem;
            color: #ff477e;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            text-shadow: 1px 1px 2px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
        }

        .subtitle {
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            color: #6c757d;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
        }

        .floating-heart {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            animation: float 2.5s ease-in-out infinite;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            display: inline-block;
        }

        .message-box {
            background: #fff;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 16px;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
            border-left: 4px solid #ff7096;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.02);
            text-align: left;
        }

        .message-box p {
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            color: #495057;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
        }

        .message-box p:last-child {
            margin-bottom: 0;
        }

        .quote {
            font-style: italic;
            font-weight: 300;
            color: #ff477e;
            margin: 20px 0;
            display: block;
        }

        .btn-surprise {
            background: linear-gradient(45deg, #ff477e, #ff7096);
            color: white;
            border: none;
            padding: 12px 28px;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            border-radius: 50px;
            cursor: pointer;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(255, 71, 126, 0.3);
            transition: transform 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s;
        }

        .btn-surprise:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(255, 71, 126, 0.4);
        }

        .hidden-note {
            display: none;
            margin-top: 20px;
            padding: 15px;
            background: #fff0f3;
            border-radius: 12px;
            color: #ff477e;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            animation: slideDown 0.5s ease-out forwards;
        }

        /* Animasi */
        @keyframes fadeIn {
            from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(20px); }
            to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
        }

        @keyframes float {
            0% { transform: translateY(0px); }
            50% { transform: translateY(-10px); }
            100% { transform: translateY(0px); }
        }

        @keyframes slideDown {
            from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(-10px); }
            to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div class="container">
        <div class="floating-heart">💖</div>
        <h1>Semangat Kerjanya!</h1>
        <div class="subtitle">Sebuah pesan kecil untuk harimu yang hebat</div>

        <div class="message-box">
            <p>Halo sayang, cuma mau ingetin kalau kamu itu hebat banget. Terima kasih ya sudah selalu berjuang, kerja keras, dan gak gampang menyerah.</p>
            <p>Gak apa-apa kalau hari ini terasa capek atau melelahkan. Istirahat sejenak kalau butuh, minum air yang cukup, dan jangan lupa makan siang ya!</p>
            <p>Ingat, apa pun yang kamu hadapi di tempat kerja hari ini, kamu pasti bisa melewatinya. Aku selalu mendukung dan bangga sama kamu di sini.</p>
        </div>

        <span class="quote">"Setiap langkah kecil kerja kerasmu hari ini, adalah jembatan menuju masa depan indah kita."</span>

        <button class="btn-surprise" onclick="showNote()">Klik Kalau Capek ✨</button>
        
        <div id="surpriseNote" class="hidden-note">
            Pukpuk! Semangat terus ya, pulangnya aku tungguin. <i>I love you more each day!</i> 🫶
        </div>
    </div>

    <script>
        function showNote() {
            var note = document.getElementById("surpriseNote");
            if (note.style.display === "block") {
                note.style.display = "none";
            } else {
                note.style.display = "block";
            }
        }
    </script>
</body>
</html>
